{"tid":1478117,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李嘉誠今日的潛台詞 — 「因果由國，容港治己」","createTime":"2019-08-16T11:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:29:52.000Z","uid":290176,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8209a37245d59c30a5721e501d7c9e44fb4ca5ff","tid":1478117,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"引文:「......第二款載於《明報》，其實更有意思，寫著「最好的<span style=\"color: red;\">因</span>，可成最壞的<span style=\"color: red;\">果</span>，愛自<span style=\"color: red;\">由</span>，愛中<span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>，愛包<span style=\"color: red;\">容</span>，愛香<span style=\"color: red;\">港</span>，愛法<span style=\"color: red;\">治</span>，愛自<span style=\"color: red;\">己</span>」八大句，中間另加一個特大的禁止「暴力」LOGO。真的很有趣，這確實是兩邊都可以解讀。直觀可解成為政府及警察要市民停止暴力，要愛國愛港，又要兼容並包、維持法治等，如他們每天在電視上所說。<br />\n<br />\n但我看到的是，好似隱藏式的情報密碼般。我只是個人覺得，超人的台詞，怎麼也沒可能這麼簡單。如果這八大句只拿每句的最後一個字，會有這樣的一個上下聯：「因果由國，容港治己」。大意可為，當今亂局的原因由國家而起，不如容許香港管治自己吧。聽下去，難道不順耳嗎？文法工整，又一語中的。......」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%BD%9B%E5%8F%B0%E8%A9%9E-%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25BD%259B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A9%259E-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A2%25BC%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0UtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=398208df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25BD%259B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A9%259E-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A2%25BC%2F&h=fde81a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%BD%9B%E5%8F%B0%E8%A9%9E-%E8%B